title: 023 - Go Digs Go
description: On today's show, Tony hosts live from the treadmill for the "Stay at Home to the Dome Fun Run Awareness Covid-19 Treadmill 24 Hour Walk to Make Money" and the guys give Tone 10 trivia questions to add an extra mile to his total, and Coach Digs calls in for a couple of assists. Check Tony's progress throughout the morning at twitch.tv/thepatmcafeeshow. Stay safe this weekend, and enjoy.
